{"tid":2412801,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"NAKD或成為第二個GME","createTime":"2021-02-18T08:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T15:19:20.000Z","uid":159103,"like":10,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"839f2fa031850d759efbacf4d775b034e860efbe","tid":2412801,"uid":159103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:47:28.000Z","msg":"Naked Brand(NAKD)其實都係一間比空頭沽空緊既公司，本身係做內衣/泳衣市場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://www.nakedbrands.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nakedbrands.com&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=2915ec07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nakedbrands.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前沽空比率(Short Ratio)大概係34%<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrA1Gu1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrA1Gu1.jpg&h=4c8017e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://fintel.io/ss/us/nakd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffintel.io%2Fss%2Fus%2Fnakd&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=d440583b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fintel.io/ss/us/nakd</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而空頭需要平倉既數目係95萬股<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71Q85Xo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71Q85Xo.jpg&h=3aa6ca39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://iborrowdesk.com/report/NAKD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiborrowdesk.com%2Freport%2FNAKD&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=26d258b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://iborrowdesk.com/report/NAKD</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你會話：人地GME一開始short成140%先夾到上$400喎，宜家得34%，夾條毛咩，但係我會話係有可能既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係NAKD股份佔比圖（source:支牛)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwBXeRx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwBXeRx.png&h=bbb4aa47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你可以見到冇乜大戶同機構持股，加埋得幾%，但係見到其他部分係佔左96%，而其他係代表散戶持有既股分佔比<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNAKD本身係一間面臨退市危機嘅公司，所以冇乜大戶/機構持股，但正正就係因為咁，散戶先可以持有96%咁多既比率，姐係話空頭雖然只係沽左34%，但散戶擁有96%既股份，只要keep住唔放，散戶係有完全既自由定價權利，繼而引發short squeeze<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且NAKD近期亦經常出現響SSR list(short sale rule list)，我夠膽肯響不久嘅將來，佢最少升3倍價（目前$1.33一股）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他參考source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://investorplace.com/2021/02/hot-stocks-three-troll-able-stocks-that-could-be-the-next-gme/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finvestorplace.com%2F2021%2F02%2Fhot-stocks-three-troll-able-stocks-that-could-be-the-next-gme%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=9b09d79b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://investorplace.com/2021/02/hot-stocks-three-troll-able-stocks-that-could-be-the-next-gme/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNAKD TG group: <a href=\"https://t.me/NAKD_Stock\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FNAKD_Stock&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=9f3dbadd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/NAKD_Stock</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己貼倉：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOVw3RU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOVw3RU.png&h=811bfcab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b3941764bd1b6b73863295f61f6dd682452c383","tid":2412801,"uid":159103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414a58b8379bbad6b946c0009b502cc62bac587d","tid":2412801,"uid":159103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a23bc1acd8382e1baa0f2e23