/><br />\n<a href=\"https://iborrowdesk.com/report/NAKD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiborrowdesk.com%2Freport%2FNAKD&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=26d258b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://iborrowdesk.com/report/NAKD</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你會話：人地GME一開始short成140%先夾到上$400喎，宜家得34%，夾條毛咩，但係我會話係有可能既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係NAKD股份佔比圖（source:支牛)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwBXeRx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwBXeRx.png&h=bbb4aa47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你可以見到冇乜大戶同機構持股，加埋得幾%，但係見到其他部分係佔左96%，而其他係代表散戶持有既股分佔比<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNAKD本身係一間面臨退市危機嘅公司，所以冇乜大戶/機構持股，但正正就係因為咁，散戶先可以持有96%咁多既比率，姐係話空頭雖然只係沽左34%，但散戶擁有96%既股份，只要keep住唔放，散戶係有完全既自由定價權利，繼而引發short squeeze<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且NAKD近期亦經常出現響SSR list(short sale rule list)，我夠膽肯響不久嘅將來，佢最少升3倍價（目前$1.33一股）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他參考source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://investorplace.com/2021/02/hot-stocks-three-troll-able-stocks-that-could-be-the-next-gme/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finvestorplace.com%2F2021%2F02%2Fhot-stocks-three-troll-able-stocks-that-could-be-the-next-gme%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=9b09d79b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://investorplace.com/2021/02/hot-stocks-three-troll-able-stocks-that-could-be-the-next-gme/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNAKD TG group: <a href=\"https://t.me/NAKD_Stock\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FNAKD_Stock&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=9f3dbadd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/NAKD_Stock</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己貼倉：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOVw3RU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/